OL,3,CBurst water main closes South
OL,4,CYorkshire school
OL,6,FA South Yorkshire school has been
OL,7,Fforced to close after a burst pipe
OL,8,Fleft it with no running water.
OL,10,FIn a message to parents, Wales High
OL,11,FSchool, near Rotherham, said it had
OL,12,F"no option" but to send children home
OL,13,Fon Tuesday.
OL,15,FIt said: "Yorkshire Water have
OL,16,Fconfirmed that engineers are already
OL,17,Fworking on the repair but it could
OL,18,Ftake between four and six hours.
OL,19,FSubsequently, we have no option but to
OL,20,Fclose the school due to health and
OL,21,Fsafety reasons."
